Achievements.Name: Cherry
Achievements.Description: Eat the Cherry that appears after eating a set number of Pac-Dots in Round 1!

Achievements.Name: Strawberry
Achievements.Description: Eat the Strawberry that appears after eating a set number of Pac-Dots in Round 2!

Achievements.Name: Orange
Achievements.Description: Eat the Orange that appears after eating a set number of Pac-Dots in Round 3 or 4!

Achievements.Name: Apple
Achievements.Description: Eat the Apple that appears after eating a set number of Pac-Dots in Round 5 or 6!

Achievements.Name: Melon
Achievements.Description: Eat the Melon that appears after eating a set number of Pac-Dots in Round 7 or 8!

Achievements.Name: Galboss
Achievements.Description: Eat the Galboss that appears after eating a set number of Pac-Dots in Round 9 or 10!

Achievements.Name: Bell

Achievements.Name: Key
Achievements.Description: Eat the Key that appears after eating a set number of Pac-Dots after Round 13!

Achievements.Name: Fruit Basket
Achievements.Description: Eat all 5 fruits (Cherry, Strawberry, Orange, Apple, Melon) in one playthrough!

Achievements.Name: All Ghosts

Achievements.Description: Eat 2 fruits and all four ghosts in succession four times in a single round!

Achievements.Description: Clear 3 Rounds in a row without eating a single ghost and without losing a life!
